Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Knowledge Representation Module Stub
Provides comprehensive knowledge representation with formal logic and semantic modeling
Enables concept extraction, relationship modeling, and knowledge inference capabilities
:End Note

Type KnowledgeRepresentationSystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    representation_language as String
    knowledge_store as KnowledgeStore
    reasoning_engine as ReasoningEngine
    query_processor as QueryProcessor
    validation_framework as ValidationFramework
    inference_engine as InferenceEngine
    evolution_manager as EvolutionManager
    mapping_engine as MappingEngine
    system_configuration as SystemConfiguration

Type KnowledgeStore is Dictionary with:
    store_id as String
    storage_type as String
    storage_backend as String
    namespace_management as NamespaceManagement
    versioning_system as VersioningSystem
    indexing_strategy as IndexingStrategy
    compression_settings as CompressionSettings
    backup_configuration as BackupConfiguration

Type Knowledge is Dictionary with:
    knowledge_id as String
    knowledge_iri as String
    knowledge_name as String
    knowledge_version as String
    knowledge_language as String
    concepts as List[Concept]
    relationships as List[Relationship]
    facts as List[Fact]
    rules as List[Rule]
    annotations as List[Annotation]
    imports as List[ImportDeclaration]
    prefixes as Dictionary

Type Concept is Dictionary with:
    concept_id as String
    concept_iri as String
    concept_name as String
    concept_type as String
    super_concepts as List[Concept]
    sub_concepts as List[Concept]
    equivalent_concepts as List[Concept]
    disjoint_concepts as List[Concept]
    concept_expressions as List[ConceptExpression]
    concept_axioms as List[ConceptAxiom]
    annotations as List[Annotation]

Type Relationship is Dictionary with:
    relationship_id as String
    relationship_iri as String
    relationship_name as String
    relationship_type as String
    domain as List[Concept]
    range as List[Concept]
    super_relationships as List[Relationship]
    sub_relationships as List[Relationship]
    equivalent_relationships as List[Relationship]
    relationship_characteristics as RelationshipCharacteristics
    relationship_axioms as List[RelationshipAxiom]

Type Fact is Dictionary with:
    fact_id as String
    fact_iri as String
    fact_name as String
    fact_type as String
    concept_assertions as List[ConceptAssertion]
    relationship_assertions as List[RelationshipAssertion]
    same_facts as List[Fact]
    different_facts as List[Fact]
    annotations as List[Annotation]

Type Rule is Dictionary with:
    rule_id as String
    rule_type as String
    rule_content as RuleContent
    rule_annotations as List[Annotation]
    rule_source as RuleSource
    rule_confidence as Float
    logical_strength as String

Type ReasoningEngine is Dictionary with:
    engine_id as String
    reasoning_type as String
    reasoner_implementation as String
    supported_profiles as List[String]
    inference_capabilities as List[InferenceCapability]
    consistency_checking as ConsistencyChecking
    entailment_checking as EntailmentChecking
    classification_engine as ClassificationEngine
    realization_engine as RealizationEngine

Type QueryProcessor is Dictionary with:
    processor_id as String
    query_languages as List[QueryLanguage]
    query_optimizers as List[QueryOptimizer]
    result_formatters as List[ResultFormatter]
    caching_system as CachingSystem
    query_analytics as QueryAnalytics

Type ValidationFramework is Dictionary with:
    framework_id as String
    validation_rules as List[ValidationRule]
    validation_engine as ValidationEngine
    quality_metrics as List[QualityMetric]
    validation_reports as List[ValidationReport]
    compliance_checking as ComplianceChecking

Type InferenceEngine is Dictionary with:
    engine_id as String
    inference_algorithms as List[InferenceAlgorithm]
    inference_metrics as List[InferenceMetric]
    inference_validation as InferenceValidation
    inference_optimization as InferenceOptimization
    cross_reference_management as CrossReferenceManagement

Type EvolutionManager is Dictionary with:
    manager_id as String
    evolution_history as List[EvolutionEvent]
    change_management as ChangeManagement
    version_control as VersionControl
    impact_analysis as ImpactAnalysis
    rollback_capabilities as RollbackCapabilities

Type MappingEngine is Dictionary with:
    engine_id as String
    mapping_algorithms as List[MappingAlgorithm]
    mapping_rules as List[MappingRule]
    mapping_validation as MappingValidation
    mapping_optimization as MappingOptimization
    cross_reference_management as CrossReferenceManagement

Type SystemConfiguration is Dictionary with:
    config_id as String
    system_parameters as Dictionary
    performance_settings as PerformanceSettings
    security_settings as SecuritySettings
    integration_settings as IntegrationSettings
    monitoring_settings as MonitoringSettings

Process called "create_knowledge_representation_system" that takes config as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "represent_knowledge" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and knowledge_input as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "extract_and_formalize_concepts" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and input_knowledge as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "identify_and_model_relationships" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and concept_extraction as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "formalize_facts_and_rules" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and knowledge_analysis as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_knowledge_inference" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and inference_query as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "validate_knowledge_representation" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and representation_data as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "query_knowledge_base" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and query_specification as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "update_knowledge_base" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and update_specification as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "create_knowledge_representation_monitoring_system" that takes configuration as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "execute_knowledge_representation_analysis" that takes system as Dictionary and query as Dictionary returns Dictionary 